These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, pall-mall, aristoff, havana
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, lemonade, 7up
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, coach, social-worker, dressmaker
1. the accountant is the havana-smoker##1
2. the social-worker is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the havana-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the coach is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
6. the dressmaker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
7. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the dressmaker is between the person drinking 7up and the bongani-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar         | havana      | bongani | pall-mall | aristoff |
| Beverage   | lemonade | soy-milk  | coffee   | 7up    |
| Job     | accountant     | social-worker    | dressmaker    | coach      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, r&b, techno, classical
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, musician, designer, bartender
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold, amaryllis, daffodil
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
2. the fan of classical is the designer##1
3. the fan of techno is in an even position##4
4. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the musician##1
7. the social-worker is between the fan of classical and the fan of r&b##2
8. the bartender is between the musician and the fan of techno##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre         | classical | techno   | r&b | indie  |
| Job   | designer     | social-worker | bartender  | musician |
| Flower     | daffodil        | amaryllis  | marigold    | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, azalea, marigold, aconite
House: palace, farmhouse, ranch-style, colonial
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, november, september
1. the colonial house is between the person who growslily and the person who growsaconite##2
2. the farmhouse house is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
6. the ranch-style house is between the person who growsazalea and the palace house##2
7. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Flower          | lily | azalea   | aconite     | marigold     |
| House   | farmhouse  | colonial | ranch-style   | palace  |
| Birthday     | september      | august | november | may |

