.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, 7up, water
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, german, american, indian
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, chess, canasta
1. the indian is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing whist##1
4. the german is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
5. the indian is the person playing whist##1
6. the person drinking 7up is the pakistani##1
7. the american is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | water   | 7up     | lemonade |
| Nationality   | american  | indian      | pakistani        | german     |
| Game         | chess | whist | canasta | backgammon   |

