.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, lavender, lilac, grey
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, paramedic, dancer, nurse
1. the person who likes grey is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who likes lilac is in an odd position##4
3. the fisherman is the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the paramedic is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the fisherman is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the dancer##3
9. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Color   | pink   | grey   | lilac | lavender |
| Beverage         | sprite      | mirinda | soy-milk      | hot-chocolate |
| Job     | paramedic | fisherman        | nurse       | dancer  |

