.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, roller, tram, trike
House: ranch-style, palace, craftsman, tower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, country, funk, r&b
1. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the fan of dubstep is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the palace house is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
8. the tower house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Transport    | tram   | trike      | roller       | train |
| House   | ranch-style | tower | craftsman     | palace |
| Music-Genre     | r&b     | country  | dubstep | funk |

