.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, iris, begonia, aconite
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, domino, backgammon
City: rome, nizza, hamburg, new-york
1. the person traveling to hamburg is the person playing bridge##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is between the person playing backgammon and the person traveling to rome##2
3. the person playing backgammon is the person who growsiris##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
5. the person who growsamaryllis is in an even position##4
6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
7. the person playing bridge is the person who growsamaryllis##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Flower      | begonia   | aconite          | iris | amaryllis        |
| Game   | domino     | mah-jongg | backgammon   | bridge     |
| City           | rome | nizza         | new-york         | hamburg |

