.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, skateboarding, snowboarding, climbing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, orchid, balloon-flower, dahlia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, crime, horror, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
6. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Sport         | skateboarding | water-polo      | snowboarding       | climbing    |
| Flower           | orchid  | balloon-flower  | dahlia | bellflower |
| Movie-Genre   | sports      | horror | crime         | epic    |

