.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, roller, quad-bike, bus
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, mexican, indian, brazilian
House: wooden, ranch-style, townhouse, craftsman
1. the russian is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the russian##3
3. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the russian##3
4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
6. the craftsman house is on the right of the russian##1
7. the russian is on the right of the person driving the train##1
8. the mexican is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
9. the brazilian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Transport   | roller         | train  | quad-bike     | bus         |
| Nationality        | brazilian | mexican | russian | indian         |
| House      | ranch-style         | townhouse  | wooden   | craftsman |

