.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, hiking, skydiving, baking
4 different games are played: go, monopoly, whist, domino
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, mauve, grey, chestnut
 1. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 2. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the person playing whist is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
 6. the person who likes chestnut is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing monopoly is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
10. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | chess  | skydiving    | hiking | baking    |
| Game   | go | whist | monopoly  | domino |
| Color           | grey   | chestnut    | lavender        | mauve   |

