.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, zinnia, bellflower, marigold
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, bike, tram
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, board-games, baking, video-games
1. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
4. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
9. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Flower      | azalea                | marigold  | zinnia | bellflower   |
| Transport           | tram | airplane | quad-bike   | bike |
| Hobby   | board-games         | hiking     | video-games     | baking |

