.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
House: farmhouse, wooden, gothic-revival, victorian
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, horse, cat
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, 7up, coffee
1. the wooden house is on the left of the victorian house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person drinking tea is between the owner of the cat and the person drinking coffee##2
6. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
7. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| House          | gothic-revival    | wooden  | victorian  | farmhouse |
| Pet   | cat | goldfish | goat | horse |
| Beverage   | 7up    | tea     | coffee    | hot-chocolate |

