The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, teacher, videographer, paramedic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, epic, crime, zombie
1. the person watching epic movies is between the alhambra-smoker and the fisherman##2
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the videographer is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the teacher##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
7. the fisherman is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
8. the videographer is the ritmeester-smoker##1
9. the paramedic is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching scientific movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar      | ritmeester | alhambra      | tiparillo  | dannemann    |
| Job   | videographer   | teacher | paramedic | fisherman |
| Movie-Genre           | zombie      | crime       | epic   | scientific      |

