.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, october, august, may
4 different pets are kept: horse, fish, rabbit, goat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, electronic, punk
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in may and the fan of folk##2
3. the fan of house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the owner of the goat is between the fan of folk and the owner of the horse##2
7. the fan of house is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
9. the fan of folk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | july    | august | october  | may  |
| Pet   | rabbit | fish       | goat | horse |
| Music-Genre         | electronic   | folk      | punk | house       |

