4. the person playing canasta is the farmhouse house##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
6. the victorian house is the dannemann-smoker##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
8. the havana-smoker is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Game      | canasta      | domino | bridge     | billiard    |
| House   | farmhouse | victorian      | futuristic | gothic-revival |
| Cigar           | dunhill   | dannemann  | ritmeester     | havana |

