.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
City: marseilles, colone, nizza, paris
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, lime, zucchini, asparagus
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, accountant, musician, firefighter
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
2. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
3. the firefighter is on the far left##1
4. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
5. the person traveling to colone is between the accountant and the person eating zucchini##2
6. the designer is the person eating asparagus##1
7. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| City    | nizza    | colone     | marseilles    | paris        |
| Food       | zucchini   | eggplant | lime | asparagus |
| Job   | firefighter | musician      | accountant    | designer   |

