.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, chess, snooker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, reggae, blues, disco
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, roller, subway, car
1. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person driving the roller and the person playing snooker##2
3. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
4. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person playing snooker is the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Game          | billiard | snooker  | backgammon   | chess    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues     | disco | reggae |
| Transport   | subway   | car | van | roller   |

