6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
