.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
City: liverpool, prague, venice, marseilles
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, almond-milk, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, house, folk, hip-hop
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
4. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to prague is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking water##2
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the fan of folk is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
8. the fan of house is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| City    | venice    | prague    | liverpool  | marseilles |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda | water | almond-milk      |
| Music-Genre     | house   | reggae        | hip-hop   | folk       |

 